{"tid":280373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人旺角街頭唱歌劇   網民讚bravo：唔想聽大媽廣場舞！","createTime":"2017-06-12T04:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T07:41:18.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6462c35e8857f9c35084d973f6ad4c44bbc55cd1","tid":280373,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497239661_8950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497239661_8950.jpg&h=c646f19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497240628_ee39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497240628_ee39.jpg&h=d9c192bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角西洋菜街行人專用區一帶，經常被唱歌跳舞的「大媽」、大叔「佔領」，一眾街頭表演甚至會「爭地盤」，惟因表演者質素參差，令一些途人開始對該區域避之則吉。6月10日「生於亂世」facebook專頁上載2段外國人在旺角街頭表演歌短片，不少網民大讚表演有水準，值得推薦，有人直言「五音不全大媽差一億班」、「呢啲先係藝術呀，大媽個啲叫噪音呀！」亦有人諷刺地稱表演者似有收取打賞，應要找入境處執法，又問到「拎左working visa 未呀」。<br />\n<br />\n片段中分別有一男一女演唱「聖母頌」，以及一名男士演唱「善變的女人」，三人身穿簡便裝束，該女士甚至身穿人字拖，表演時以小型喇叭播放音樂。有曾聽過該表演的網民留言，稱可現場購買表演者的CD。<br />\n<br />\n【網民點講】<br />\nHei Yeung：點都好，個個都想要睇D高素質的表演<br />\nIp Adryan Ho-yan：睇相佬有冇發老脾？<br />\nPaul Yip：好勁，真功夫<br />\nDuke Lilomei：哩（呢）啲先佩（配）香港。What a breath of fresh air!掃走啲江湖雜耍不倫不類嘅妖孽就啱喇。"},{"pid":"2d4961b62e7749a3933b2f08ed829e6ddbebad40","tid":280373,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"第二張真係，做乜撚"},{"pid":"9db906c9172a80de4329a0e11e22beb1070faea1","tid":280373,"uid":52102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"個個on9啖罐阿叔 玩黎玩去都個味"},{"pid":"7595262f8f5f44678676fc297e452dd72dc9e370","tid":280373,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"住係果到真係慘"},{"pid":"c0865cd013858dadddaa52886d654095ca4e22c3","tid":280373,"uid":6124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個on9啖罐阿叔 玩黎玩去都個味</blockquote><br />\n個阿叔惡撚到條馬路好似佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e495b85d53d5ae56c5d1c07ed77684aa6b4dc20a","tid":280373,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c471e9c866acd2a35b342ec0db6979e7fa49d4a","tid":280373,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"寧願睇大媽舞, 都唔想睇鬼佬囉<br />\n<br />\n當然最好係本土少女kpop cover dance"},{"pid":"59db24e976b1678493f51ffff497aaadc7bb81f2","tid":280373,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"旺角夜晚我多數見到又廟街既本土文化搬左過黎<br />\n班中佬老女人係到載歌載舞<br />\n呢樣確實係本土廟街文化黎<br />\n但一向口講支持本土既連登仔<br />\n就覺得呢d係老土 失禮野"},{"pid":"d36c4529d159e28c447d1e671c9ef9422e33bbcd","tid":280373,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"thank you"},{"pid":"497e793913375d04585af439777a206f21984105","tid":280373,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"Duke Lilomei<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c337b90facdf3c62f9c37323c04f7e9669b51518","tid":280373,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"班妖孽拍西遊記"},{"pid":"ef2f8888e6a06e0bb8e70a89c2cc13208f1daebf","tid":280373,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Duke Lilomei<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}